snippet.title: Duke Forces [Star Wars mod]
snippet.description:
Duke Forces is a Star Wars modification for Duke Nukem 3D made by DeeperThought (Duke Nukem: Attrition, Duke Plus). You play as Duke Nukem mixed in with the standard Duke Nukem 3D alien enemies as well as enemies from Star Wars: Dark Forces. It also features lightsaber combat which is the highlight of the mod.

At the moment there are no maps designed for it so you can either play through the standard episodes or try out the exclusive episode which features a bunch of random user maps specifically chosen by DeeperThought.

Download link: http://www.moddb.com/mods/duke-forces/downloads/duke-forces-11
